  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of FST-100 (0.1% dexamethasone)
      Ophthalmic Suspension in the treatment of suspected acute adenoviral conjunctivitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
